data.description: Welcome to your dream one-level living home with a spacious bonus room over a 2-car garage. This stunning home boasts superb upgrades such as a stylish tiled master bath, new flooring, and an amazing outdoor space with a lake view. The home is adorned with gas fireplace, hardwood and carpeting on the second level. Step outside and be with a space perfect for entertaining and enjoying the outdoors, a small walk and you are easily boating,fishing or skipping rocks! With its prime location, you'll appreciate the convenient walkability to the nearby lake, boat ramp, Lock 4 Mountain bike trail, and park. This home will not disappoint!
